<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạḥfẓny fy rḍạk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạḥfẓny fy rḍạk .. bạqy ạ̉yạm ʿmry
 ạjdẖbny mn wrạk .. (ạjdẖbny wạ̉nạ ạ̉jry)2
 2- ạmlạ̉ny bạlạ̉sẖwạq .. nḥwk ḥbyb qlby
 mty̱ mty̱ ạ̉rạk .. (ʿnd ạnthạʾ drby)2
 3- ạ̉yqẓny llṣlwạt .. ʿqlny yạ rby
 wạḥmny mn ạldẖạt .. (wkn ynbwʿ ḥby)2
 4- yạ sạkn fy ʿlạk .. yạ mn lh ạảmry
 qd qlt lạ ạ̉nsạk .. (mn msk ms ʿyny)2
 5- hyỷny llbrkạt .. ạskb skyb ḥbk
 wạns kl ạlly fạt .. (hạ ydy ạ̉ḍʿhạ fy ydk)2
 6- ln ạ̉ṭlqk yạ yswʿ .. mạ lm tbạrkny
 wlạ hạrḍy̱ bḥạlẗ ạljwʿ .. (ftʿạl wạ̉sẖbʿny)2</lyrics>
<author>ạlạ̉b mkạry ywnạn, ạlạ̉b mkạry ywnạn</author>
